<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Escape Hub</title>
    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:wght@500;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600&display=swap");

      :root {
        --ink: #1c1510;
        --paper: #f7f1e8;
        --accent: #ce5f3a;
        --accent-dark: #7a3520;
        --shadow: rgba(23, 15, 10, 0.18);
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Space Grotesk", "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", "Yu Gothic", sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #fff7ea 0%, #e5d2b9 45%, #b79b7f 100%);
        color: var(--ink);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 20px 18px 28px;
      }
      main {
        width: min(980px, 100%);
        display: grid;
        align-content: start;
        gap: 8px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-family: "Fraunces", "Yu Mincho", serif;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        line-height: 1.18;
      }
      .hero {
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%, rgba(244, 220, 180, 0.55), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 85% 0%, rgba(206, 95, 58, 0.18), transparent 45%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 100%);
        border-radius: 22px;
        padding: 18px 22px 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 34px var(--shadow);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 8px;
      }
      .hero::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: -30% -10% auto -10%;
        height: 90%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 35%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6), transparent 65%);
        opacity: 0.6;
        pointer-events: none;
      }
      .hero p {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(28, 21, 16, 0.75);
        max-width: 560px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .hero p:last-of-type {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .games {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        display: grid;
        align-content: start;
        gap: 2px;
      }
      .games li {
        margin: 0;
      }
      .game-card {
        display: block;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 30px var(--shadow);
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      }
      .game-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 32px rgba(23, 15, 10, 0.24);
      }
      .game-inner {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
      }
      .game-visual {
        border-radius: 16px;
        height: 130px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .game-visual::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(130deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25), transparent);
      }
      .game-visual::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 10px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px dashed rgba(28, 21, 16, 0.22);
      }
      .scene {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
      }
      .piece {
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background-size: contain;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-position: center;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 12px rgba(23, 15, 10, 0.2));
      }
      .scene-room .window {
        left: 10%;
        top: 18%;
        width: 32%;
        height: 40%;
        background-image: url("1/assets/safe-closed.svg");
        border-radius: 12px;
      }
      .scene-room .shelf {
        left: 8%;
        bottom: 12%;
        width: 60%;
        height: 28%;
        background-image: url("1/assets/shelf.svg");
      }
      .scene-room .key {
        right: 14%;
        top: 18%;
        width: 20%;
        height: 20%;
        background-image: url("1/assets/key.svg");
      }
      .scene-room .memo {
        right: 12%;
        bottom: 16%;
        width: 28%;
        height: 22%;
        background-image: url("1/assets/memo.svg");
      }
      .scene-train .train-window {
        left: 12%;
        top: 20%;
        width: 38%;
        height: 40%;
        background-image: url("2/assets/window.svg");
        border-radius: 18px;
      }
      .scene-train .door {
        right: 12%;
        top: 18%;
        width: 26%;
        height: 60%;
        background-image: url("2/assets/door.svg");
        border-radius: 12px;
      }
      .scene-train .monitor {
        left: 18%;
        bottom: 18%;
        width: 26%;
        height: 16%;
        background-image: url("2/assets/monitor.svg");
      }
      .game-meta {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: rgba(28, 21, 16, 0.7);
      }
      .game-title {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.28rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .game-desc {
        margin: 4px 0 6px;
        color: rgba(28, 21, 16, 0.75);
      }
      .play {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 6px 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        width: fit-content;
      }
      .play span {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .game-card[data-game="room"] .game-visual {
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(206, 95, 58, 0.5), transparent 60%),
          linear-gradient(140deg, #f4e5cf, #d0b59a);
      }
      .game-card[data-game="train"] .game-visual {
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(80, 130, 180, 0.45), transparent 60%),
          linear-gradient(140deg, #e3ecf6, #b7c7da);
      }
      @media (min-width: 760px) {
        .game-inner {
          grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 240px) minmax(0, 1fr);
          align-items: center;
        }
        .game-visual {
          height: 150px;
        }
      }
      .note {
        color: rgba(28, 21, 16, 0.7);
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin: 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="note">Escape Hub</p>
        <h1>脱出への一歩</h1>
        <p>短時間で遊べる脱出ゲームのアーカイブ。気になるシーンへ飛び込もう。</p>
      </section>

      <ul class="games">
        <li>
          <a class="game-card" data-game="room" href="/escape/1/">
            <div class="game-inner">
              <div class="game-visual" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="scene scene-room">
                  <span class="piece window"></span>
                  <span class="piece shelf"></span>
                  <span class="piece key"></span>
                  <span class="piece memo"></span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="game-title">ワンルーム脱出（#1）</p>
                <p class="game-desc">身近な部屋に隠された小さな違和感を追って、最後の鍵を探す。</p>
                <div class="game-meta">
                  <span>所要: 5-7分</span>
                  <span>難易度: Easy</span>
                </div>
                <div class="play"><span>▶</span> Start</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="game-card" data-game="train" href="/escape/2/">
            <div class="game-inner">
              <div class="game-visual" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="scene scene-train">
                  <span class="piece train-window"></span>
                  <span class="piece door"></span>
                  <span class="piece monitor"></span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="game-title">電車内脱出（#2）</p>
                <p class="game-desc">静かな車内に残された手がかりを繋ぎ、閉ざされた扉を開く。</p>
                <div class="game-meta">
                  <span>所要: 6-8分</span>
                  <span>難易度: Normal</span>
                </div>
                <div class="play"><span>▶</span> Start</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
